summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Water Department and authorizing the sale and removal of alder and other hardwood timber, and certain additional materials incidental to thinning and salvage from City-owned lands in Townships 21, 22 and 23 North, Range 7 East, W.M., and Townships 21, 22 and 23 North, Range 8 East, W.M., and township 22 North, Range 9 East, W.M., in the Cedar River Watershed under contract with Masao Nakaso.
